ActionPlanModel, AlarmModel, AlertConfigModel, AlertMessageModel, BeaconModel, CabinetStyleModel, CameraModel, CameraTemplateModel, CommConfigModel, CommLinkModel, ConnectionModel, ControllerTableModel, DayMatcherModel, DayPlanModel, DetectorModel, DeviceActionModel, DMSModel, DomainModel, EncoderStreamModel, EncoderTypeModel, EventConfigModel, FlowStreamModel, GateArmArrayModel, GateArmTableModel, GpsModel, GraphicModel, IncAdviceTableModel, IncDescriptorTableModel, IncidentDetailModel, IncLocatorTableModel, LaneMarkingModel, LaneUseMultiModel, LCSArrayModel, LCSTableModel, MapExtentModel, ModemModel, MonitorStyleModel, MsgLineTableModel, MsgPatternTableModel, ParkingAreaModel, PermissionModel, PlanPhaseModel, PlayListModel, R_NodeDetectorModel, RampMeterModel, RoadAffixModel, RoadModel, RoleDomainModel, RoleModel, SignConfigModel, SignDetailModel, StationModel, SystemAttributeTableModel, TagReaderModel, TimeActionModel, TollZoneModel, UserTabModel, VideoMonitorModel, VidSrcTemplateModel, WeatherSensorModel, WordTableModel
public abstract class ProxyTableModel<T extends SonarObject> extends AbstractTableModel implements ITableModel
Table model for IRIS proxies. This model allows a RowSorter to be used with the table for sorting and filtering.
Author:
Douglas Lau
